region kingdomofsaints
parent dream
longname The Kingdom of Saints
msg
A kingdom where pagan worship is outlawed and magic scorned. Dispite this there is said to
be much advanced knowlege known to it, outside the realms of sorcery and superstition.
The kingdom has a severe shortage of gold and thus prefers outsiders to pay debts in the metal,
however it is rich in iron and copper ore, aswell as emeralds, though it's emerald production
has recently sharply decreased due to an unknown reason.
endmsg
end
region kingdomofsaintsborder
parent kingdomofsaints
longname The Kingdom of Saints Border
msg
A kingdom where pagan worship is outlawed and magic scorned. Dispite this there is said to
be much advanced knowlege known to it, outside the realms of sorcery and superstition. To the
east of here lies the Valley of Gehennom. To the north and south is unknown wilderness.
endmsg
end
