region stbartholomew
parent kingdomofsaints
longname Town of St.Bartholomew
msg
The town of St. Bartholomew is the capital of the Kingdom of Saints.
Situated between two mountain ranges rich in iron and copper ore St.
Bartholomew is well protected and well supplied with minerals useful
in wartime production. St. Bartholomew boasts a world class
bank, a well stocked libary, and one of the only two power generation 
plants in existance, as well as the only working centerfuge throughout the
explored world.
endmsg
end

